<br>
I think the debate over ITR is long gone.  It's on rare occasion that anyone even rants about it anymore.  So to that end, I'm not sure why it needed to be removed.  It's bee a fairly quiet area of MMDN for a while now.<br>
<br>
I'd vote to put the forum back with a new title.  Maybe call it &quot;On-Goings&quot; or something like that.  Define the rules to say:  This forum is to post for Open raids.  You may find people who respect your schedule, but be warned that MANY will use it to jump your raid.  USE AT YOUR OWN RISK!<br>
<br>
